{"type": "article", "id": 24074, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-03-18T07:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 1954, "name": "包装"}, {"id": 25075, "name": "DOMINO BOXES"}, {"id": 25076, "name": "villahomecollection"}, {"id": 25077, "name": "Holy Trinity"}, {"id": 25078, "name": "Louie Rigano"}, {"id": 25079, "name": "Yeji Yun"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 47, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702135453FWMIGoz3nXl5r4KJ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>hammock and rocking chair </h2>\n<p>这是由 3 位来自印度浦那的学生设计的椅子，她们将摇椅和吊床结合起来，用了黑铁结构和不同的编织方式，在椅子下面增加了弧形的支撑，使它可以摇晃。椅子的结构是圆形的，像一个月亮门。它其实用了两根黑铁框，窄的一边是可提椅子的扶手，而宽的一边是座位。3 位学生想在两周内完成一把椅子，而这把椅子也有巧妙和聪明的地方。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021209551URMS80OdGCBcopi.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120956MseArcyE70GVQiKJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.40375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120956ArwK98uIL3DNsqGV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.09625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120957p9DVLKx5u02kmyEc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.99125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021209573yzpHZMvoXW6Eru8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.36625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>BIRK COFFEE TABLE BY DOMINO BOXES</h2>\n<p>这个椭圆形的桌子是一张咖啡桌，桌面的一头是绿色的，用来做咖啡托盘。向内划开后则能发现一个圆形的粉色储物柜，可以放一些毛线等小的物品。在原本简单普通的咖啡桌里隐藏了一些小心思。桌面和桌腿都非常圆润，让这张桌子显得轻盈小巧。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120958s6QmfRu07KyqGWzP.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120958IVgYGZxJvf93D8ke.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021209583X6s7lYBU8Q4GuE0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120959oDMh7T8brzxEyqtK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120959goTVjQmSU1BEI8N0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>The Vara by Holy Trinity</h2>\n<p>这款灯保持了一种简单的几何感，像是圆环和线的结合。一根斜线充当灯管倾斜穿过了圆形的灯座，与桌面保持锐角，在圆形灯座下面扣了一个可移动的环，相当于一个固定位置的基座。圆环是黑色的，与白色的直线灯管构成强烈的对比，突出了点和线条的结合。这款灯可由 APP 控制，目前还没有上市。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121000wY280vDGjAqkslf4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6647619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121000drkojnNblDOmQSJ0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6647619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121001O6qv2UHho7p9MbPA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6647619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070212100181uBsgqDeKnhCWk0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6647619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121002FSanBkws1GJ5orhi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Shadow Curtains by Louie Rigano</h2>\n<p>这是一款丝制的窗帘，在阳光的照射下窗帘本身印出了自然的光影，通过深浅来区分，就像花草树木的影子印在了窗帘上，非常漂亮。窗帘整体是紫色的，上面混合了一些蓝色或黄色，带给人更丰富的变化的自然。设计师来自美国新泽西，这是他的第二代，<a href=\"http://www.louierigano.com/Shadow-Curtains\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121002xLAhOtI7UzGv83XQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121003XGM0waVQ2LfUjony.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121004BdqUC5PgrJ8bWnma.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121004CsKQ9718AilxoVgz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121005wtT7DnLjlUXrVQHu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>GAETANA magazine rack by villahomecollection</h2>\n<p>这是一个放杂志的架子，它有一个像篮子一样的外形。上面是一个手提杆，而下面有两个小格子去放上几本杂志，整体保持对称的形态，简单优雅。这种设计增加了它的灵活性，你可以带着它从客厅到卧室，这种轻松的感觉与杂志正好很搭配。可以选择三种材料，红木、橡木和橡木和橄榄木的搭配。设计师来自米兰，他们做了很多类似的木质小家具，售价 200 美元，<a href=\"https://www.crowdyhouse.com/shop/gaetana-magazine-rack/\">这里是购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121005LSYCxsRAeHwhcnqK.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121006AGgrt63EXCaVO0Tz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121006kQIzw7G6xXpERbTS.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121007g7nDRbA9VEtxfZ3L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67978723\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121007t45Jushec8mQTUyz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>TIME TO BLOSSOM by Yeji Yun</h2>\n<p>这套化妆品来自韩国，包装上的插画来自汉城的插画师 Yeji Yun。他将各类动物拟人化，它们穿着人的衣服，做着人的活动，出现了游泳的兔子，看书的猫，骑自行车的大象，理发的狮子，煎蛋的鸡等种种有趣的生活场景，有个性而又有故事。使用动物的元素当然是为了体现出天然无害，在这些故事里又能引起你更多的联想。<a href=\"http://seeouterspace.com/studio/\">这里是工作室链接</a>，他有很多类似有趣的插画。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121008tivKX8l1zCV39qPS.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021210086xFvM8Z7OUbhVei4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121008JYwSrTuLMxqEeita.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121009ArZF07a5fKYiIUmG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33888889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121009TVGneU1Mr0CbpuQs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}